Date: Sat, 11 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] gmp: skip runtime long long tests for Gentoo GCC15/binutils 2.46

Upstream-Status: Inappropriate [Gentoo GCC15/binutils 2.46 host compatibility]
Signed-off-by: Aurélien DESBRIERES <aurelien@hackers.camp>
